(42129, 3, 0, 'zhCN', '要是我们在暗炉城，我一定会把你扔进秩序竞技场的，大使先生。现在只好拿铁炉堡里最黑暗的地下城凑合一下。'),
(42129, 4, 0, 'zhCN', 'The cult must have someone in the city to coordinate this kind of attack. That only leaves one suspect, Ambassador Slaghammer!'),
(42129, 5, 0, 'zhCN', 'If we were in Shadowforge City, I would have you tossed into the Ring of Law for your transgressions, Ambassador. The darkest dungeons of Ironforge will have to do for now.'),
(42131, 0, 0, 'zhCN', 'Muradin has a point. If you cannot govern your own people, you have no place at this table.'),
(42153, 0, 0, 'zhCN', '我愿意去，$c。我在主人计划中应尽的职责已经完成。'),
