(52941, 2, 0, 'zhCN', 'Allow me ta show you something I discovered. Now where\'d I see dat satchel?'),
(52941, 3, 0, 'zhCN', 'Help yourselves. It be suicide for a scout to walk around wit\' so much weighing me down.'),
