(92980, 0, 0, 'zhCN', '玛维为什么要放了我们？只可能是一个原因……'),
(92984, 0, 0, 'zhCN', 'Do not speak to me of old times, Altruis. You betrayed Illidan. You betrayed us all!'),
(92984, 1, 0, 'zhCN', 'He was fighting it, as we all do. He needed us to have faith in him, Altruis.'),
(92984, 2, 0, 'zhCN', 'He made the hard choices. He sacrificed EVERYTHING. What did you give?'),
(92984, 3, 0, 'zhCN', 'You heard the Warden. We are the only ones who can defeat the Legion. We MUST survive this place.'),
(92984, 4, 0, 'zhCN', 'You trust no one and believe in nothing, Altruis. You are a leader with no followers.'),
(92985, 0, 0, 'zhCN', 'Just like old times, eh Kayn?'),
(92985, 1, 0, 'zhCN', 'After ten-thousand years of imprisonment, Illidan succumbed to the fel energy within. When he was freed, he was not in his right mind.'),
(92985, 2, 0, 'zhCN', 'You followed Illidan blindly, like a dog. Even when he lost his way.'),
(92985, 3, 0, 'zhCN', 'I fought as hard as the rest of you! But I did not murder thousands of innocents.'),
(92985, 4, 0, 'zhCN', 'Fool! You would trust the warden? She hates us almost as much as the Legion.'),
(92986, 0, 0, 'zhCN', '燃烧军团来了。'),
(92986, 0, 1, 'zhCN', 'The Legion is here.'),
(93011, 0, 0, 'zhCN', '都听到了吧？让我们去找到那块钥石。'),
