(96473, 0, 0, 'zhCN', '军团的意志必将实现。'),
(96494, 0, 0, 'zhCN', '军团万岁！'),
(96494, 1, 0, 'zhCN', 'The fel you wield will not be enough.'),
(96494, 2, 0, 'zhCN', 'Demon hunters? How did you get here?'),
(96494, 3, 0, 'zhCN', 'Die, Illidari fool.'),
(96494, 4, 0, 'zhCN', 'You dare attack us here?!'),
(96494, 5, 0, 'zhCN', 'Invaders. Warn the Brood Queen!'),
(96499, 0, 0, 'zhCN', 'The fel lord is just ahead.'),
(96503, 0, 0, 'zhCN', '谢谢你。来吧，兄弟们……回去战斗！'),
(96590, 0, 0, 'zhCN', '我要揍扁你！'),
(96652, 0, 0, 'zhCN', '$n，等等……我控制不了这股力量。'),
(96652, 1, 0, 'zhCN', '啊啊啊！'),
(96653, 0, 0, 'zhCN', '祝你们好运。我会把其他人送上去的，$n。'),
(96654, 0, 0, 'zhCN', '$n，你成功了！'),
(96655, 0, 0, 'zhCN', '我最后一次看见考瓦斯的时候，她在桥上杀出了一条血路。'),
(96655, 1, 0, 'zhCN', '我感觉到了……更致命的恶魔能量。'),
(96657, 0, 0, 'zhCN', '|TInterfaceIconsspell_fire_ragnaros_molteninferno.blp:20|t$n|cFFFF0000|Hspell:185828|h[复燃]|h|r了一个邪能烧灼者！'),
(96672, 0, 0, 'zhCN', 'That was too close for my liking. $n, the demon\'s power is yours.'),
(96675, 0, 0, 'zhCN', '升降机马上就来。其他人都在上面等你。'),
(96682, 0, 0, 'zhCN', '跟我走，恶魔猎手。我能给予你们无穷的力量！'),
(96682, 1, 0, 'zhCN', '守望者想让我们彻底烂死在这儿。干嘛还要帮他们呢？'),
(96726, 0, 0, 'zhCN', '等等！住手！你……你不是恶魔……'),
(96726, 1, 0, 'zhCN', '迷雾散去了，我又能看清真相了。谢谢你，$pc。如果你愿意到我的老店来，我们或许可以进一步谈谈。'),
(96726, 2, 0, 'zhCN', 'The fog has lifted and I can see the truth once more. Thank you, $pc. If you would join me at my old shop, perhaps we can speak further.'),
(96754, 0, 0, 'zhCN', '鲜血的气味让幽灵们感到饥渴了。'),
(96754, 1, 0, 'zhCN', '新乘客……新灵魂。我可以带你们深入冥狱深渊，只要一点小报酬：你们的血肉。'),
(96754, 1, 1, 'zhCN', '进入冥狱深渊的人都得付出血的代价。挣扎吧……但我必将拿到我的报酬！'),
(96754, 2, 0, 'zhCN', '站起来吧，仆人！为我们讨还血债！'),
(96754, 2, 1, 'zhCN', 'Spirits! Sweep these mortals into the tides!'),
(96754, 2, 2, 'zhCN', '就算我得不到报酬，幽灵们也会的！'),
(96754, 3, 0, 'zhCN', 'The flesh burdens the soul. A nuisance that must be flayed from your bones'),
(96754, 4, 0, 'zhCN', '|TInterfaceIconsAbility_Warlock_ImprovedSoulLeech:20|t %s开始|cFFFF0000|Hspell:194325|h[粉碎]|h|r$n。'),
(96754, 5, 0, 'zhCN', '海拉会让你们付出代价的……最终，所有人都得付出代价……'),
(96754, 5, 1, 'zhCN', '生命……死亡……我只是永恒潮汐中的一朵小水花……'),
(96754, 5, 2, 'zhCN', 'Helya will make you pay in the end, everyones pays...'),
(96756, 0, 0, 'zhCN', '你们的灵魂将永远在冥界之海中徘徊！'),
(96756, 0, 1, 'zhCN', 'Mortals... Your wretched kind murdered MY people... destroyed MY kingdom! Now you, too, will know what it feels like to lose EVERYTHING!'),
(96756, 0, 2, 'zhCN', 'Mortals... I fell to your wretched kind once before. It WILL NOT happen again!'),
(96756, 1, 0, 'zhCN', '灵魂大海中的又一滴水！'),
(96756, 1, 1, 'zhCN', 'FLEE, COWARDS!'),
(96756, 1, 2, 'zhCN', 'COWER BEFORE ME!'),
(96756, 2, 0, 'zhCN', '凡人……你们杀害我的人民……摧毁我的王国！我一直在等待这个机会，将你们所做的一切加倍奉还！'),
(96756, 2, 1, 'zhCN', 'The winds of the frozen north still howl in these veins!!'),
(96756, 3, 0, 'zhCN', '懦弱的蛆虫！'),
(96756, 4, 1, 'zhCN', '北地的寒风仍在这些藤蔓间呼啸！'),
(96756, 5, 0, 'zhCN', '冥界的阴影都听从我的意志！'),
(96756, 5, 1, 'zhCN', 'Vengeance!'),
(96756, 5, 2, 'zhCN', 'I will carve a new crown from your bones!'),
(96756, 6, 0, 'zhCN', '冥狱的阴影，狠狠侵蚀那块钢铁吧！'),
(96756, 7, 0, 'zhCN', '还没完呢……纳格法尔号会来……找你们的……'),
(96756, 7, 1, 'zhCN', 'Not... again... HARBARON! CAST THEIR SOULS INTO THE TIDES!'),
(96756, 7, 2, 'zhCN', 'You have not won... You have only... secured your own doom...'),
(96756, 8, 0, 'zhCN', 'Your souls will drift for eternity in the tides of the underworld!'),
(96756, 8, 1, 'zhCN', 'Another drop in the sea of souls!'),
(96759, 0, 0, 'zhCN', '你们都会后悔闯入我的国度的。'),
(96759, 1, 0, 'zhCN', '你们已经走的够远了，该去死了。'),
(96759, 2, 0, 'zhCN', '你们的命运降临了！'),
(96759, 2, 1, 'zhCN', '拥抱你们的命运吧，蠢货！'),
(96759, 3, 0, 'zhCN', '你会为此付出代价的。'),
(96759, 3, 1, 'zhCN', '我的耐心正在消失。'),
(96759, 3, 2, 'zhCN', '不！这不可能！'),
(96759, 3, 3, 'zhCN', '你到底是什么样的生物？？'),
(96759, 3, 4, 'zhCN', '这就是奥丁认可的生命？'),
(96759, 4, 0, 'zhCN', 'An eternity of agony awaits you.'),
(96759, 4, 1, 'zhCN', '我要像淹死老鼠一样淹死你们。'),
(96759, 4, 2, 'zhCN', '别动！'),
(96759, 4, 3, 'zhCN', '别乱动！'),
(96759, 5, 0, 'zhCN', 'Your soul will not find shelter here.'),
(96759, 5, 1, 'zhCN', 'Begone to the next life.'),
(96759, 6, 0, 'zhCN', 'It is finished. I banish your weak mortal souls forever more.'),
(96759, 7, 0, 'zhCN', 'Do you think you have won? You have merely survived the storm... The seas are unstoppable.'),
(96759, 8, 0, 'zhCN', '|TInterfaceIconsinv_misc_leatherscrap_17.blp:20|t%s的近战范围内没有敌人，开始施放|cFFFF0000|Hspell:198520|h[飞翼打击]|h|r！'),
(96759, 9, 0, 'zhCN', '你们以为自己赢了？这只是一场风暴而已……大海是不可阻挡的。'),
(96847, 0, 0, 'zhCN', '但愿玛维的决定是正确的，恶魔猎手。去吧——我来守住阵线。'),
